<p>LIKE (–ø–æ–∏—Å–∫):</p>
<div class="language-sql highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span><span style="color:#B06;font-weight:bold">SELECT</span> * <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">FROM</span> Customers <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">WHERE</span> LastName <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">LIKE</span> <span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">'</span><span style="color:#D20">A%</span><span style="color:#710">'</span></span>
